      • authorDataParser

        public void authorDataParser(java.lang.String path,
                             java.lang.String uri)
        This method parses all the required csv files and forms a hash map, having key as author name and value as author data object. finally these objects are written into mongoDB
        Parameters:
        path - : path of the csv files
        uri - : connection string of the mongoDB, where the data should be finally stored
